    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require CCTV anywhere that looks after children and vulnerable people",
        "additional_details": "This could help provide evidence to support any claims or suspicions giving families reassurance and closure.",
        "background": "Make it law that anywhere that looks after children or vulnerable people -  from disabled people, to pensioners, from nursery children to people with Alzheimer's disease - is required to install CCTV on their premises. ",
